  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dca\u0da9\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dd1 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another person was killed after being shot with a gun",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A hospital spokesman said that another person who was receiving treatment at the Gampaha District General Hospital after being injured in the shooting incident that took place in front of the Gampaha High Court on the 27th, died early this morning.",
        "Piyathilaka Thisera, the neighbor of Basnayaka Appuhamila, who resided in Kotugoda, Maduruvita, has died.",
        "Mr. Pas Podda died earlier in this shooting incident and two others who were injured by gunshots are receiving treatment at the Gampaha Hospital, said Hospital Director Specialist Dr. Saman Pathirana in response to a query."
      ],
